# Zcash Tools for Creators (Tipping)

Creators can receive tips and donations using tools built on the **Zcash network**. These platforms allow audiences to support creators directly using **ZEC**, while preserving strong financial privacy through shielded transactions.

This page highlights tools that enable **Zcash-based tipping for creators**.

---

## Zcash.me

![Zcash.me Logo](https://zcash.me/favicon.ico)

**Website:**  
https://zcash.me

### Description
**Zcash.me** is a public directory of Zcash users that allows creators to associate a simple identity with their Zcash address. It makes it easier for supporters to discover and tip creators directly.

### Features
- Public directory of Zcash users
- Simple identity linked to a Zcash address
- Enables discovery of creators within the Zcash ecosystem
- Allows direct ZEC tipping
- Creator profiles and community leaderboards
- Social discovery features

---

## TipZ

![TipZ Logo](https://tipz.cash/favicon.ico)

**Website:**  
https://tipz.cash

### Description
**TipZ** is a creator tipping platform that enables supporters to send **private ZEC tips** to creators through dedicated tip pages. Tips are delivered using shielded Zcash transactions to ensure strong privacy.

### Features
- Dedicated creator tip pages (`tipz.cash/[username]`)
- Private ZEC tipping using shielded transactions
- ZIP-321 payment QR codes for easy wallet payments
- Cross-chain tipping (ETH, USDC, USDT, SOL converted to ZEC)
- Real-time creator dashboard
- Encrypted messages attached to tips
- Creator discovery directory
- 0% platform fees
